115
00:07:22,399 --> 00:07:23,759
between South and Dahan.

116
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,800
Shipping speeds

117
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:25,839
can at least double.

118
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,680
